{
  "texts": [
    "Knowledge sharing and exchange should be encouraged in policy implementation to promote international experience sharing.",
    "Drawing on successful cases and lessons learned from other countries and regions can help optimize domestic biomaterial policies and practices.",
    "Policy implementation is a dynamic process that requires continuous improvement and optimization.",
    "The government should continuously learn and reflect, adjust policies and measures promptly based on actual results, and ensure that policies align with industry needs.",
    "In recent years, the construction industry's growing global focus on energy efficiency has drawn considerable interest, primarily from using bio-based materials."
  ]
}